com.nerjal.json.parser

Class ArrayState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nerjal.json.parser.AbstractState
      • com.nerjal.json.parser.ArrayState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserState

    public class ArrayState
extends AbstractState
    The StringParser JSON array parsing state class.
    Can hold other elements, in order to fill in the parsed array. Thus, can open any kind of other states.
    Closes on ']'
    Author:
    nerjal
